quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,104,"Si …ďe mbiamaa: "ngree e ko Alla Jippini kon e faade e Nulaa…óo on", …ďe mbi'a:"Yonii min ko min tawri baabiraa…ďe amen …ďe", e hay si baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe ngandaa hay e huunde …ďe peewataa?!"
  5,105,"Eeheymon gooŇč…óin…ďe ! Hino fawii on pittaali mon …óin! Lorratah on majju…óo si on peewi. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal; O Humpita on kon ko ngollatno…óon."
  5,106,"Eeheymon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe ! Mba…óee seedee hakkunde mon, si maayde nden arii go…ó…óo e mon, tuma wasiyagol, [seedee…ďe] …ói…óo nuun…óu…ďe jeyaa…ďe e mo'on, si tawii on yehii ka leydi masiibo maayde yanii e mon. Darnon …ďe ka batte julude, …ďe ngoo…óndira Alla, si on ciikkatikm …ďe ngostotaako fii …óuum coggu, hay si laatike joomiraawo badindiral, "min cuu…óataa seedee Alla on, minen ontuma [si min mba…óii …óum], haray men njeyaama e bakkondin…ďe …ďe"."
  5,107,"Si tawaama won de …ďe kaan di e bakkaatu, ko wo…ó…ďe …ói…óo darotoo darnde ma…ď…ďe nden, hara ko jeyaa…ďe e haandu…ďe e hettugol , …ďe ngoo…óndira Alla : "Pellet, ko seedee amen on …ďuri jojjude seedee ma…ď…ďe on ; min njawtaani keeri. Minen ontuma [si men mba…óii …óum], haray men njeyaama e too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"."
  5,108,"Ko …óum …óoo …ďuri …ďa…ótaade nde …ďe ngaddata seedee e hoore nden …óon, maa …ďe kula nde woondoore ruttetee …ďaawo woondoore ma…ď…ďe nden. Alla Fewnataa yaltu…ďe …óoftaare …ďe"